files.name: .editorconfig
files.content:
# top-most EditorConfig file
root = true

# Unix-style newlines with a newline ending every file
[*]
end_of_line = lf
insert_final_newline = false
max_line_length=120

# Indentation override for all JS under lib directory
[*.{js,ts}]
indent_style = space
indent_size = 4

files.name: .gitignore
files.content:
# Node Modules
dist/
node_modules/

# Coverages
coverage/

# Benchmarking
benchmark/results
*.log

# Misc
.Rhistory
.idea/
.DS_Store
.vscode
.settings

# Do not put the generated documentation in master
docs/

files.name: .travis.yml
files.content:
language: node_js
node_js:
  - "12"
  - "14"
  - "15"
after_success:
  - npm run coveralls

files.name: README.md
package-lock.json
package.json
tsconfig.json
files.content:
{
  "compilerOptions": {
    "sourceMap": true,
    "inlineSources": false,
    "inlineSourceMap": false,
    "noEmit": false,
    "declaration": true,
    "stripInternal": true,
    "downlevelIteration": true,
    "esModuleInterop": true,
    "importHelpers": false,
    "moduleResolution": "node",
    "noFallthroughCasesInSwitch": true,
    "removeComments": true,
    "target": "es6"
  },
  "include": [
    "src",
    "test"
  ],
  "typedocOptions": {
    "entryPoints": ["src/index.ts"],
    "out": "docs",
    "name": "Chrono",
    "readme": "none",
    "includeVersion": true,
    "theme": "default"
  }
}
